Reality TV stars attended a party at the Big Brother house to celebrate The National Trust's controversial move to open the iconic building to the public.

Model Sophie Anderton and cage fighter Alex Reid were among the many former housemates to take a trip down memory lane.

Reid, 38, the ex-husband of media personality Katie Price, said he was thrilled to return to the site of his win in 2010.

